      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2023 R1 employed under ISO 9001-certified QMS. Full V&V test suite executed per ASME V&V 10.1 with documented pass records. Software version control, change management, and regression testing logs archived in traceable configuration management system. Independent audit completed by third-party QA reviewer."
