      "rationale": "Benchmark problems including Timoshenko beam bending, Hertzian contact, and large-deformation elastoplastic patch tests executed. Analytic solutions matched to within 0.1% relative error for all linear cases. Code-to-code comparison with FDA FEA reference implementation confirmed consistent QoI predictions within 0.5% across all three model instantiations (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes)."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
