      "rationale": "Systematic mesh convergence study conducted across four refinement levels (coarse to ultra-fine). Richardson extrapolation applied; grid convergence index (GCI) < 0.8% for stiffness and < 1.2% for yield force QoIs. Final mesh selected at refinement level 3 where QoI change between successive levels < 0.5%. Contact zone mesh density independently verified."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 5,
