      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/morrison-equivalency-criteria",
      "rationale": "Direct traceability established between each FEA model input and corresponding experimental measurement. Material properties matched to coupon tests from same production lot as test constructs. Geometric model updated with per-specimen CMM measurements. Contact parameters calibrated against fixture compliance measurements. Formal input-equivalency matrix completed and reviewed; no unresolved discrepancies."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
