      "rationale": "Quantitative validation metric E/uval computed for all three QoIs per ASME V&V 10 framework. Stiffness: E/uval=0.82 (<1.96 threshold). Yield force: E/uval=1.14 (<1.96). Force at 40 mm: E/uval=1.31 (<1.96). All QoI percent differences < 7% (within 10% acceptance bound). Validation uncertainty uval includes experimental measurement uncertainty, model parameter uncertainty, and numerical uncertainty combined in quadrature. Full uncertainty budget tabulated."
