      "rationale": "Three QoIs (construct stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement) directly correspond to regulatory submission requirements and clinical failure modes identified in FDA guidance. QoI selection justified in COU description with explicit linkage to device safety and effectiveness endpoints. Sensitivity analysis confirms these QoIs are the primary drivers of model output variance (cumulative Sobol total-order index > 0.95 for identified input parameters)."
    },
